MeetupsRegistrationBaseImpl
public class MeetupsRegistrationModelImpl
extends com.liferay.portal.model.impl.BaseModelImpl<MeetupsRegistration>
implements MeetupsRegistrationModel

The base model implementation for the MeetupsRegistration service. Represents a row in the "SN_SMILE_MeetupsRegistration" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

This implementation and its corresponding interface MeetupsRegistrationModel exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in MeetupsRegistrationImpl.

Author:
Brian Wing Shun Chan
